{"tid":1941571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［武肺］新加坡關閉酒吧,戲院及娛樂場所至4月30日","createTime":"2020-03-24T13:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T13:53:27.000Z","uid":185424,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"90ec9812c1f4389e263b9c1674c40f8b7b871995","tid":1941571,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"新加坡同香港一樣面臨第二波爆發<br />\n<br />\n佢地終於要落重手<br />\n<br />\n禁止補習同興趣班<br />\n禁止宗教聚會<br />\n禁止10人以上的聚會<br />\n<br />\n商場同博物館可繼續開放，但要確保one person per 16 sq m<br />\n所有3月27日或之後離開新加坡的外國居民如因為武漢肺炎入院，必須以一個非資助的價錢付款<br />\n<br />\n違反14日隔離令需面臨五萬港元的罰款或不多於6個月的監禁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但繼續學照返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔使戴罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後又係時候報下數<br />\n新加坡558 （今日增加49宗，32宗係外地輸入）<br />\n香港 385<br />\n<br />\n坡仔，睇下你地得戚得幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVOnMcD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVOnMcD.png&h=880b8ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/all-entertainment-venues-in-singapore-to-close-gatherings-outside-work-and-school?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_campaign=STFB&amp;utm_source=Facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fsingapore%2Fhealth%2Fall-entertainment-venues-in-singapore-to-close-gatherings-outside-work-and-school%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_campaign%3DSTFB%26utm_source%3DFacebook&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=a30cc4c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/all-entertainment-venues-in-singapore-to-close-gatherings-outside-work-and-school?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_campaign=STFB&amp;utm_source=Facebook</a>"},{"pid":"7c20c79838ac6700fbeafc8b37236596ca585d41","tid":1941571,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply